casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
John Antonya MOSS, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 156616
COA: 338877 Supreme Court of Michigan. October 19, 2018

Order

On order of the Chief Justice, the motion of plaintiff-appellee to extend the time for filing its supplemental brief is GRANTED. The supplemental brief will be accepted as timely filed if submitted on or before November 14, 2018.
